'From Squeakland 3.8.5976 of 25 August 2004 [latest update: #293] on 2 September 2004 at 4:05:14 pm'!"Change Set:		BorderedTextBigger-nkDate:			2 September 2004Author:			Ned KonzChanges the Text(border) prototype to a bigger nicer font."!!TextMorph class methodsFor: 'parts bin' stamp: 'nk 9/2/2004 16:03'!borderedPrototype	| t |	t _ self authoringPrototype.	t fontName: 'BitstreamVeraSans' pointSize: 24.	t autoFit: false; extent: 250@100.	t borderWidth: 1; margins: 4@0."Strangeness here in order to avoid two offset copies of the default contents when operating in an mvc project before cursor enters the morphic window"	t paragraph.	^ t! !"Postscript:"PartsBin clearThumbnailCache.!